00:35:45.102 --> 00:35:47.560 align:middle line:84%
>> I'd love to tell you a story
about a woman that I worked

00:35:47.560 --> 00:35:48.360 align:middle line:90%
with.

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:51.370 align:middle line:84%
She came in to me after a
lecture on heart disease,

00:35:51.370 --> 00:35:53.530 align:middle line:84%
