00:35:54.820 --> 00:35:56.110 align:middle line:90%
And her story went like this.

00:35:56.110 --> 00:35:57.820 align:middle line:84%
She had just had
her third medicine

00:35:57.820 --> 00:36:00.800 align:middle line:84%
