00:36:04.130 --> 00:36:05.510 align:middle line:90%
She'd gained 30 pounds.

00:36:05.510 --> 00:36:08.950 align:middle line:84%
She was stress-eating because
part of her day-to-day

00:36:08.950 --> 00:36:12.700 align:middle line:84%
was taking care of her husband
who had chronic lung disease,

00:36:12.700 --> 00:36:15.800 align:middle line:84%
and it was just
spiraling out of control.

00:36:15.800 --> 00:36:18.070 align:middle line:84%
We didn't put her on
any specific program,

00:36:18.070 --> 00:36:19.510 align:middle line:84%
but we talked about
the importance

00:36:19.510 --> 00:36:22.300 align:middle line:84%
of her taking care of herself,
and eating a whole foods diet,

00:36:22.300 --> 00:36:24.200 align:middle line:90%
and getting some movement.

00:36:24.200 --> 00:36:27.310 align:middle line:84%
I didn't hear back from
her for nine months.

00:36:27.310 --> 00:36:29.650 align:middle line:84%
