I didn't recognize her.

00:36:29.650 --> 00:36:31.460 align:middle line:90%
She had lost 30 pounds.

00:36:31.460 --> 00:36:32.483 align:middle line:90%
I said, wow.

00:36:32.483 --> 00:36:33.775 align:middle line:90%
