things, and re-engage.

00:36:58.330 --> 00:37:00.280 align:middle line:84%
And here was what was
beautiful about that.

00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:02.620 align:middle line:84%
She was off of all of her
blood pressure medicines,

00:37:02.620 --> 00:37:04.540 align:middle line:84%
