acid-blocking medicines.

00:37:06.520 --> 00:37:08.110 align:middle line:84%
She had stopped her
antidepressants.

00:37:08.110 --> 00:37:09.800 align:middle line:84%
She had stopped
her sleeping pills.

00:37:09.800 --> 00:37:11.950 align:middle line:84%
She had stopped her
anti-inflammatories

00:37:11.950 --> 00:37:13.240 align:middle line:90%
for her joints.

00:37:13.240 --> 00:37:16.390 align:middle line:84%
